## Status and Stability

mdz is an **early proof of concept** with:

**Strengths:**
- Comprehensive test coverage (181 fixtures)
- Well-defined parsing behavior
- Production use in Fuz documentation
- Self-documenting (this spec is written in mdz)

**Limitations:**
- Limited feature set (no lists, blockquotes, tables)
- No attribute/prop support for components/elements
- API may change based on real-world usage
- Early adopters should expect breaking changes

**Version:** Current as of Fuz v0.150.0

**Feedback:** Issues and suggestions welcome at https://github.com/ryanatkn/fuz/issues
